      "title": "Today is power cut hour",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Public Utilities Commission says that the power cut will be reduced to one hour today (28) due to the restoration of the first power generator of the Lakwijaya Power Plant in Norochchole and the addition of it to the national power system."
      ],
